OL,4,Cheartbreaking message on 35th birthday
OL,6,F"I wish someone would just have a
OL,7,Fheart and come forward with the
OL,8,Finformation I desperately need."
OL,10,FThe 21-month old was living on Kos
OL,11,Fwith Kerry and her family, who had
OL,12,Fmoved from England earlier in 1991 to
OL,13,Fstart a new life on the Greek isle.
