OL,3,CMother of Ben Needham issues
OL,4,Cheartbreaking message on 35th birthday
OL,6,FOn the morning of Wednesday July 24th,
OL,7,F1991, Kerry - who was only 19 years
OL,8,Fold herself at the time - was working
OL,9,Fat a nearby hotel while her dad Eddie
OL,10,Fwas helping local workmen renovate a
OL,11,Fderelict farmhouse in the remote
OL,12,Fhamlet of Irakles. The farmhouse is
OL,13,Freached via a single-track dead end
OL,14,Froad, with just a handful of homes
OL,15,Fmaking up the tiny community.
OL,17,FKerry's mum Christine decided to take
OL,18,FBen in a push chair from the caravan
OL,19,Fin which they were living nearby, to
OL,20,Fthe farmhouse, to see Eddie.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/11
