OL,4,Cheartbreaking message on 35th birthday
OL,6,FSouth Yorkshire Police received Home
OL,7,FOffice grants to carry out two
OL,8,Fexcavations at the farm - in 2012 and
OL,9,F2016 - but despite a huge effort,
OL,10,Finvolving Greek volunteers, nothing
OL,11,Fwas found to conclusively prove Ben's
OL,12,Fwhereabouts.
OL,14,FAt the end of the three-week 2016
OL,15,Fexcavation, South Yorkshire Police
OL,16,Fannounced it was their professional
OL,17,Fopinion that Ben had died on the the
OL,18,Fday he disappeared, in an accident
OL,19,Fwith a digger, which was being used
OL,20,Fnearby.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/11
