OL,4,Cheartbreaking message on 35th birthday
OL,6,FIn September 2011 Calendar's Mark
OL,7,FWitty and cameraman Simon White
OL,8,Ftravelled with Kerry and Eddie Needham
OL,9,Fto the Albanian border with Greece, to
OL,10,Ffollow up information on a man
OL,11,Fsuspected of being Ben. He agreed to a
OL,12,Fmouth swab which was handed over to
OL,13,FSouth Yorkshire Police at Manchester
OL,14,FAirport. It was negative.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/11
