OL,3,CMother of Ben Needham issues
OL,4,Cheartbreaking message on 35th birthday
OL,6,FIn 2015 a man came forward in
OL,7,FThessalonika, Greece, who was also
OL,8,Fconvinced he was Ben. Mark and Simon
OL,9,Ftravelled with Kerry, her mum
OL,10,FChristine and daughter Leighanna to
OL,11,Fmeet him - but their hopes were dashed
OL,12,Fwhen a DNA test proved no link.
OL,14,FOnly this year a Danish man came
OL,15,Fforward believing he was the missing
OL,16,Fboy - but yet again there was no match.
OL,18,FMany other claims and messages go un-
OL,19,Freported with most going direct to a
OL,20,Fsmall dedicated team which runs
OL,21,Ffacebook.com/helpfindben
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/11
