OL,3,CMother of Ben Needham issues
OL,4,Cheartbreaking message on 35th birthday
OL,6,FThe social media page has attracted
OL,7,Fthousands of messages over the years,
OL,8,Fsome of which have been investigated
OL,9,Fby them and ITV Calendar together,
OL,10,Fwith updates sent to police where
OL,11,Fnecessary.
OL,13,FKerry added: "There are some people on
OL,14,FKos that definitely know what happened
OL,15,Fto Ben and I don't know how they can
OL,16,Fsleep at night knowing the torment I
OL,17,Fgo through year after year. I will
OL,18,Fnever give up searching for the truth
OL,19,Feven if it kills me , we deserve to
OL,20,Fknow the truth"
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/11
